# Neo Contact Desk

Neo Contact Desk is a modern contact form validation project created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- Stylish split-screen contact form design
- Dark glassmorphism user interface
- Name validation
- Email validation using regex
- Message validation
- Live character counter
- Error messages for invalid inputs
- Success message after valid submission
- Reset button
- Responsive design for mobile screens

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository.
2. Open the project folder in VS Code.
3. Open "index.html" in Chrome browser.
4. Fill the form and test validation.

## Validation Rules

- Name should not be empty and must contain at least 3 characters.
- Email should not be empty and must follow proper email format.
- Message should not be empty and must contain at least 20 characters.

